    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Live individual of Dipsas aparatiritos sp. nov. in Parque Nacional General de Division Omar Torrijos Herrera photographed in the wild and not collected. Photography by Kevin Enge." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805202" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Holotype (USNM 579828) of Dipsas aparatiritos sp. nov. showing a dorsum and b venter. Ruler units in cm. Photographs by James Poindexter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805203" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Holotype (USNM 579828) of Dipsas aparatiritos sp. nov. showing a dorsum of head and b chin shields and c lateral view. Ruler notches denote mm. Photographs by James Poindexter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805204" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Paratype (USNM 579829) of Dipsas aparatiritos sp. nov. showing a dorsum and b venter. Ruler units in cm. Photographs by James Poindexter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805205" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Paratype (USNM 579829) of Dipsas aparatiritos sp. nov. showing a dorsum of head and b chin shields and c lateral view. Ruler notches denote mm. Photographs by James Poindexter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805206" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure7>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Illustration of the head scales of a Dipsas aparatiritos sp. nov. (USNM 579810). Drawings by Shannon Bowley Christensen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805207" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure8>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Hemipenes of Dipsas aparatiritos sp. nov. USNM 579815 a sulcate face b, d lateral faces c asulcate face. Photographs by James Poindexter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805208" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Phylogeny of 20 species of Dipsas using the best ML tree. Black circles denote strong nodal support (≥ 0.95 PP and ≥ 0.70 ML bootstrap). See Sheehy (2012) for further details on the outgroup taxa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805201" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Photographs of species of Dipsas previously subsumed under D. temporalis a D. aparatiritos sp. nov. from Cerro Gaital, Anton, Cocle province, Panama b D. temporalis ZSFQ 5063 from Durango, Esmeraldas province, Ecuador c D. temporalis ZSFQ 5062 from Durango, Esmeraldas province, Ecuador." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805210" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure9>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Map of locality data for Dipsas aparatiritos sp. nov. (red showing range, circles marking specimens included in this paper) and updated range data for D. temporalis (yellow showing range, triangles marking specimens included in this paper)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805209" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1145.96616.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Four individuals of Dipsas aparatiritos sp. nov. intertwined on one plant at Parque Nacional General de Division Omar Torrijos Herrera. Photograph by Noah Carl." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/805211" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

